    SELECT TOP(1) [n].[Id], [n].[Achievements], [n].[CategoryId], [n].[CreatedAt], [n].[Description], [n].[NominatorId], [n].[NomineeId], [n].[Status], [n].[YearQuarterId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[IsActive], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TeamId], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a0].[Id] AS [Id1], [a0].[AccessFailedCount] AS [AccessFailedCount0], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp] AS [ConcurrencyStamp0], [a0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt1], [a0].[Discriminator] AS [Discriminator0], [a0].[Email] AS [Email0], [a0].[EmailConfirmed] AS [EmailConfirmed0], [a0].[IsActive] AS [IsActive0], [a0].[LockoutEnabled] AS [LockoutEnabled0], [a0].[LockoutEnd] AS [LockoutEnd0], [a0].[Name] AS [Name0], [a0].[NormalizedEmail] AS [NormalizedEmail0], [a0].[NormalizedUserName] AS [NormalizedUserName0], [a0].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash0], [a0].[PhoneNumber] AS [PhoneNumber0], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed] AS [PhoneNumberConfirmed0], [a0].[SecurityStamp] AS [SecurityStamp0], [a0].[TeamId] AS [TeamId0], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled] AS [TwoFactorEnabled0], [a0].[UserName] AS [UserName0], [t].[Id] AS [Id2], [t].[DirectorId], [t].[ManagerId], [t].[Name] AS [Name1], [t].[TeamLeadId], [c].[Id] AS [Id3], [c].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt2], [c].[Description] AS [Description0], [c].[Name] AS [Name2], [c].[isActive] AS [isActive1], [y].[Id] AS [Id4], [y].[EndDate], [y].[IsActive] AS [IsActive2], [y].[Quarter], [y].[StartDate], [y].[Year]
    FROM [Nominations] AS [n]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [n].[NominatorId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [n].[NomineeId] = [a0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Teams] AS [t] ON [a0].[TeamId] = [t].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [n].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [YearQuarters] AS [y] ON [n].[YearQuarterId] = [y].[Id]
    WHERE [n].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]
LEFT JOIN [Approvals] AS [a1] ON [t0].[Id] = [a1].[NominationId]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3], [t0].[Id4]"
